    "body": "![Image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/38d09a50-3abf-4301-b1f0-dbc107e3b86b)\n\n### Duplicate Check\n\n- [x] I confirm I searched for existing reports and found no duplicates.\n\n### Describe the Bug\n\n![Image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/d8d9fa30-a695-4e56-b3c3-85dfbba39a30)\n\n![Image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/0b508c51-af6e-49c5-8a38-18f23203c168)\n\nAt first it's strange because within the local track the track design changes to video, and in the YouTube library it's the Cambas track. The problem isn't that, but rather what happens when it changes to video It suddenly freezes and I can't unfreeze it until I go online to the YouTube playlist and change it.\n\nIt's strange and weird; it often drives me crazy because I can't go back to listening to the music I was listening to before because it glitched when it switched from canvas to video And the problem is that there's no way to reverse it except by forcing me to go online. \n\n\n### Steps to Reproduce\n\nThis usually happens when the canvas is activated in the YouTube playlist, but when I go to the local playlist, the video appears.\n\n### Expected Behavior\n\nI apologize for the inconvenience. If there were a way to select video and chat options in real time, I'd love that, but if not, then we'll have to revert to the previous playback method Normalcy, even so, I know it's difficult because YouTube and Spotify update to prevent that.\n\n### App Version\n\n1.0.4\n\n### Android Version\n\nAndroid 15\n\n### Device Model\n\nSamsung a15\n\n### Custom ROM\n\n- [ ] I am using a custom ROM\n\n### Custom ROM Name (if applicable)\n\n_No response_\n\n### Screenshots (optional)\n\n_No response_\n\n### Log / Error Details\n\n_No response_",
