    "body": "### Duplicate Check\n\n- [x] I confirm I searched for existing reports and found no duplicates.\n\n### Describe the Bug\n\nWhenever i play downloaded songs in complete offline mode (no internet connection) and if i turn the screen off, the app crashes. Tried this again with internet connection and sometimes it does crash and sometimes it doesn't\n\n### Steps to Reproduce\n\n1. Download any song \n2. Close the app and turn your wifi or data off.\n3. Open the app and play the song through downloads section \n4. Turn the screen off\n\n### Expected Behavior\n\nI expected the song to play like usual in the background after closing the screen but instead the app just completely closes and there is no entry of this in crash logs\n\n### App Version\n\n1.0.4\n\n### Android Version\n\nAndroid 12\n\n### Device Model\n\nRedmi Note 9 Pro\n\n### Custom ROM\n\n- [ ] I am using a custom ROM\n\n### Custom ROM Name (if applicable)\n\n_No response_\n\n### Screenshots (optional)\n\n_No response_\n\n### Log / Error Details\n\n_No response_",
